response.original_title: Super Why!: Goldilocks and the Three Bears and Other Fairytale Adventures
response.overview: Sometimes a challenge feels too big! Sometimes a clue seems too small! But when it comes to the power of reading, the story of Goldilocks and the Three Bears is, of course, just right! In the fun-filled adventure Goldilocks and the Three Bears, Whyatt makes a mess in his brother Jacks room, and Jack is not happy! Can Whyatt uncover how to fix things with Jack?
response.title: Super Why!: Goldilocks and the Three Bears and Other Fairytale Adventures
